        <abstract> 
<p>Encloses an article he wrote for the <hi rend="italic">Scotsman</hi> [9 Mar 1871, p. 5].</p>  
<p>Wishes he had time to write a critique of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>. There is evidence of design and benevolence in nature. Beauty cannot be accounted for by natural selection.</p> 
        </abstract>
